<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="B" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Beetle1" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Beetle,</orth> subst., 1) insect of the genus Coleoptera: <bibl n="shak. tmp 1.2.340" default="NO" valid="yes">Tp. I, 2, 340</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. mm 3.1.79" default="NO" valid="yes">Meas. III, 1, 79</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. mnd 2.2.22" default="NO" valid="yes">Mids. II, 2, 22</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. mac 3.2.42" default="NO" valid="yes">Mcb. III, 2, 42</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. lr 4.6.14" default="NO" valid="yes">Lr. IV, 6, 14</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. ant 3.2.20" default="NO" valid="yes">Ant. III, 2, 20</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. cym 3.3.20" default="NO" valid="yes">Cymb. III, 3, 20</bibl>.<lb />2) rammer: <cit><quote>if I do, fillip me with a three-man b.</quote> <bibl n="shak. 2h4 1.2.255" default="NO" valid="yes">H4B I, 2, 255</bibl></cit> (a rammer so heavy that it requires three men to manage it).
